Don Megowan https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Don_Megowan 0 Don Megowan (May 24, 1922 – June 26, 1981) was an American actor. He played the Gill-man on land in The Creature Walks Among Us, the final part of the Creature from the Black Lagoon trilogy. Don_Megowan ( May_24_,_1922 – June_26 , 1981 ) was an_American_actor .
